The 5 best celebrity career quotes|http://www.glamour.co.za|https://www.glamour.co.za/2018/10/celebrity-career-quotes/|Celebrity Career Advice,quotes,Celebrity Quotes|2018-10-18|October||From Basetsana Khumalo to Victoria Beckham, we’ve compiled a list of our top 5 celebrity career quotes to give you motivation for the rest of the work week.



Basetsana Khumalo

“When you wake up each morning, you have to think of yourself as a brand and act accordingly. How well you do that will define the brand’s success.”

A post shared by Basetsana Kumalo (@basetsanakumalo) on Sep 10, 2018 at 8:42am PDT

Beyonce

“I strongly believe if you work hard, whatever you want, it will come to you. I know that’s easier said than done but keep trying.”

A post shared by Beyoncé (@beyonce) on Mar 22, 2018 at 12:55pm PDT

Victoria Beckham

“I believe you can achieve anything if you work hard enough to get it.”

A post shared by Victoria Beckham (@victoriabeckham) on Mar 15, 2018 at 9:51am PDT

Michelle Obama

“There is no magic to achievement. It’s really about hard work choices and persistence.”

A post shared by Michelle Obama (@michelleobama) on Oct 31, 2017 at 1:00pm PDT

Terry Pheto

“I’ve always tried to take on work that is meaningful and work that I’d be proud of in the future…”

A post shared by Terry Pheto (@terrypheto) on Nov 10, 2017 at 10:03am PST

